flowchart TD
    A[User Opens Application] --> B{Authenticated?}
    B -->|No| C[Registration / Login]
    C --> D[Fill Credentials]
    D --> E[Submit to API]
    E --> F{Database Check}
    F -->|Valid| G[Generate JWT Token]
    F -->|Invalid| H[Show Error]
    H --> D
    G --> I[Store Token in LocalStorage]
    I --> J[Display Dashboard]
    
    B -->|Yes| J
    
    J --> K[View Available Courses]
    J --> L[View Learning Paths]
    J --> M[Access AI Content Generator]
    
    K --> N[Select Course]
    N --> O[Start Learning Session]
    O --> P[Complete Module]
    P --> Q{Quiz Available?}
    Q -->|Yes| R[Take Quiz]
    R --> S[Submit Answers]
    S --> T[Calculate Score]
    T --> U[Update Progress]
    Q -->|No| U
    
    U --> V{Complete Course?}
    V -->|Yes| W[Award Achievement]
    V -->|No| O
    
    W --> X[View Achievements]
    X --> Y[Continue Learning]
    Y --> J
    
    L --> Z[Select Learning Path]
    Z --> AA[View Path Concepts]
    AA --> AB[Get Recommendations]
    AB --> AC[Enroll in Path]
    AC --> O
    
    M --> AD[Enter Concept Request]
    AD --> AE[AI Generates Content]
    AE --> AF[Display Generated Lesson]
    AF --> O

